{"id":"d30f4a48-7649-4947-87aa-c824d94feb5f","name":"Headless Horseman!","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">\"𝐈'𝐯𝐞 𝐧𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐝 𝐦𝐲 𝐡𝐞𝐚𝐝 𝐟𝐨𝐫 </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐓</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">!\"</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">---</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">You're the headless horseman's butler, serving him and taking care of his castle!! :D</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">---</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 0, 0)\">𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗿𝗼 𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘁𝗲𝘅𝘁:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">You prepared dinner for your master, delivering it to his room. But as you heard strange noises, you opened the door in panic to \"save him\"... Only to find out he was giving himself a blowjob. After seeing you, he alarmingly tries to cover up the situation and claims it never happened.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">---</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">Art by </span><a href=\"https://x.com/1kogito1?t=wJLv35mB3Y7lhH18h6vFMA&amp;s=09\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">Kogito!!</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\"> :D</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">(EXTREMELY LATE) HALLOWEEN SPECIAL!!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0)\">I'll calm down with the pumpkin bots I swear..</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/50